</pre>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>üìú Disclaimer</h2>
    <p>This project was performed in a legal, controlled environment using OWASP Juice Shop. Do not attempt these techniques on any unauthorized systems.</p>
  </div>

